data.title: All Saints, Hockerill (Church Of England)
data.meta_description: An Anglican Church of Catholic outlook, but catering for a wide variety of needs. Friendly and welcoming with a lot going on. The worship of God, and the service of his people are high priorities. Sunday Services 8:00a.m. Holy Communion 10:00 a.m. Parish Mass (Sunday School & Creche) 10.00 a.m. (1st Sunday of the month only) Parish All-age Mass). The church hall can be hired for many different social gatherings, with a licensed bar, kitchen and toilets. For bookings visit our website.
data.text:
An Anglican Church of Catholic outlook, but catering for a wide variety of needs. Friendly and welcoming with a lot going on. The worship of God, and the service of his people are high priorities. Sunday Services 8:00a.m. Holy Communion 10:00 a.m. Parish Mass (Sunday School & Creche) 10.00 a.m. (1st Sunday of the month only) Parish All-age Mass).

The church hall can be hired for many different social gatherings, with a licensed bar, kitchen and toilets. For bookings visit our website.
